Title: Series: Landscapes with Biblical and Mythological Scenes
Description: Flight into Egypt; landscape with Holy Family on a donkey in lower left corner, a river with a wooden bridge at centre, a large house at right, a city in the background. 1558 Etching
Curator's comments: This is one of a series of 12, for comment see 1922,0410.260.
